Notes: TCNJ extends win streak to four with 67-52 win over Montclair State. Kristen
McCandless matched her season-high 16 points for the Lions, while Adrienne
Warner added 11. For the Red Hawks, Jasmine Batts contributed 16 and grabbed
11 boards and Dyette Dillard chipped in 12 points.
